# OpenFGA env-var overrides for every service that consumes the centralized
# authorization store. Copy the bits you need into your service-specific .env
# (for example IAMRusty/.env, Hive/.env, Manifesto/.env, Telegraph/.env) or
# set them in your shell before running cargo / docker compose.
#
# Each service uses its own env prefix because rustycog-config namespaces
# config-file overrides per service (HIVE_*, MANIFESTO_*, TELEGRAPH_*,
# SENTINEL_SYNC_*). The double-underscore separator binds env vars onto
# nested config sections (`HIVE__OPENFGA__STORE_ID` -> `[openfga]` ->
# `store_id`).
#
# After running OpenFGA you can bootstrap a store + model with the fga CLI:
#   fga store create --name aiforall --api-url http://localhost:8090
#   fga model write --store-id <ID> --file openfga/model.fga \
#       --api-url http://localhost:8090
# then plug the generated ids below.

# ---- Hive -----------------------------------------------------------------
HIVE__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://localhost:8090
HIVE__OPENFGA__STORE_ID=
HIVE__OPENFGA__AUTHORIZATION_MODEL_ID=
# HIVE__OPENFGA__API_TOKEN=

# ---- Manifesto ------------------------------------------------------------
MANIFESTO__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://localhost:8090
MANIFESTO__OPENFGA__STORE_ID=
MANIFESTO__OPENFGA__AUTHORIZATION_MODEL_ID=
# MANIFESTO__OPENFGA__API_TOKEN=

# ---- Telegraph ------------------------------------------------------------
TELEGRAPH__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://localhost:8090
TELEGRAPH__OPENFGA__STORE_ID=
TELEGRAPH__OPENFGA__AUTHORIZATION_MODEL_ID=
# TELEGRAPH__OPENFGA__API_TOKEN=

# ---- sentinel-sync (worker) -----------------------------------------------
SENTINEL_SYNC__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://localhost:8090
SENTINEL_SYNC__OPENFGA__STORE_ID=
SENTINEL_SYNC__OPENFGA__AUTHORIZATION_MODEL_ID=
# SENTINEL_SYNC__OPENFGA__API_TOKEN=

# ---- Network-scoped overrides ---------------------------------------------
# When running inside the docker-compose network use the service hostname
# instead of localhost:
#   HIVE__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://openfga:8080
#   MANIFESTO__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://openfga:8080
#   TELEGRAPH__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://openfga:8080
#   SENTINEL_SYNC__OPENFGA__API_URL=http://openfga:8080
